content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.30 - Loading and unloading of passengers or cargo by vehicles for hire restricted

State Regulations

No vehicle for hire shall load or unload passengers or
cargo in or upon the airport at any place other than those designated by the
airport operator. Notes
